    "body": "The `testnet` command is for creating a _new_ datadir, not for resuming.\r\n\r\nOnce you've created a datadir using `lighthouse bn testnet ...`, you can just resume using `lighthouse bn`. The help menu is specific that it's for creating a _new_ datadir:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/sigp/lighthouse/blob/55680ab1d34ea7001df32573dd96277486331b21/beacon_node/src/cli.rs#L214\r\n\r\nFeel free to suggest some extra help text if you want.",
